{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|astronomy}} An [[astronomical]] [[event]] that occurs when one [[celestial object]] is [[hidden]] by another celestial object that passes between it and the [[observer]] when the nearer object appears larger and completely hides the more distant object.
# The state of being {{l|en|occult||[[hidden]], [[undetected]]}}.
